file.name: flat-object.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  description: 'A sample object containing standard properties'
  title: 'Sample: flat object'
  version: 1.3.4

components:
  schemas:

    FlatObject:
      type: object
      required:
        - id
        - name
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          format: date-time
          description: Some ID
          example: 'xyz'
        name:
          type: string
          description: 'Some name'
          example: 'Prawn'
